reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The corner of my living room above my entertainment center is a black hole, but I don't want a bunch of lights on when I'm watching TV. This lamp lights up the corner in a very unobtrusive way. You can't even see it in my photo but I have it pointing toward the walls to provide ambient light. It comes with an inline switch for on/off, warm and cool light. I prefer the cool, white light, but there's also a setting for a mix of both. Now, if I can just find the timer I bought for the power strip I have it plugged into, I'll be totally set because I can't reach the switch. I just leave it on for now; since it's LED I'm not worried about it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The reviews are user error, it is a perfectly working lamp for the price point
reviews.reviewText: The lamp works perfectly well; it has three lighting mode (white, warm, and soft white) and then you have the option to dim it from low light to bright light. I noticed people complaining about how you can’t adjust the dimness or that it’s too bright, and frankly,that seems to be user error because it dims just fine. You need to hold your finger on the power button, not pressing it, holding it. It will dim the lighting to dark and you can lift your finger and hold it again to get it brighter.The lamp is very sleek and very clean, and fits the aesthetic I was aiming for. I think people need to read the manual in order to place such criticism. I do agree that it would be nice if it came with a remote or that the cord wasn’t placed where it is, because I like having the lamp face the wall for an ambient feeling and the cord placement is an eyesore.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Perfect amount of light and easily changed if you need more or less. I like that it’s simple. I turned mine towards the wall, and like others didn’t like the cord placement. Easy fix however. There is a tiny screw that can be loosened and the light turned slightly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 21, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars This is a very elegant lamp
reviews.reviewText: Very elegant and modern lamp. Easy to assemble and works well. Took off one star because I bought it as a bedside lamp but really more suited to living areas of the house. Has three settings bright (really bright) natural and cool. All settings work well and the light on all three settings provides enough to see clearly. My only issue is that the light is a bit bright for the bedroom for me. I prefer a much more muted light source for the bedroom. That being said it is a really good product and I recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was looking for something slim so my mirror didn’t get covered up. This is perfect. Slim design. Easy touch button. Easy to assemble. Plenty bright. Had three settings that you can brighten or dim.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful accent lamp
reviews.reviewText: Put the lamp behind a small artificial bamboo potted plant and the glowing effect is breathtaking. I needed a night light that did not shine any light directly into the room since I watch TV there and mirrors are on all walls. This lamp is a perfect indirect light and gives off a very bright light if desired. The brightness is adjustable but not too great a range. The control is on the cord and its location is a little annoying for me, but then it also makes the placement of the lamp versatile. I am very happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for the a great price
reviews.reviewText: Considering how much I paid for this product, I am pleased with this. It has three different types of lighting (i.e. cool, warm, and neutral) and is powered by touch on a cord, however, the only critique that I have for this product is the level of lighting. I wish it would be a little brighter, however, I am pleased with the amount of lighting and the types of lighting that this product produces.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I ended up returning this. The light is insanely bright, despite 3 light color tones.
Product base is solid and heavy, really feels high quality. The lamp has fantastic brightness controls and adds great ambience to bookshelf.
